### 1) 正常注册
POST http://localhost:8080/api/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testuser01",
  "password": "123456"
}

### 2) 重复用户名（执行一次1后再执行）
POST http://localhost:8080/api/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testuser01",
  "password": "123456"
}

### 3) 参数非法（用户名太短）
POST http://localhost:8080/api/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "ab",
  "password": "123456"
}
